{"tid":205082,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"見到自殺post唔該比啲耐性","createTime":"2017-04-17T13:46:08.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-21T04:16:04.000Z","uid":13294,"like":40,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4f741947b14a4b3c50e72f186b8f6f57197a50f5","tid":205082,"uid":13294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T13:46:08.000Z","msg":"發現而家啲人越嚟越討厭自殺post<br />\n<br />\n因為好多人開完自殺post最都係冇做到，甚至有人開自殺post只係為左引人注意<br />\n<br />\n但係唔好忘記有一班真係暫時失去一切 同有壓力既人想上嚟尋求安慰同意見<br />\n<br />\n我地既每一句都可以對佢地造成好大影響<br />\n<br />\n如果你真係對呢啲post好反感，可以直接離開，唔洗浪費時間打字叫人地去死。咁樣只會益左班想引人注意既人<br />\n<br />\n仲有，曾經想自殺既巴絲，如果你地開完post得到啟發，可以開post多謝下同講講你地而家過成點, 作為回報同幫下其他想輕生既巴絲<br />\n<br />\n我唔想見到lihkg變成一個充滿負能量既地方"},{"pid":"11cebde6762b754abb27bd113399f28f581dffb0","tid":205082,"uid":13294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T13:56:23.000Z","msg":"認真post冇人理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb0bae88bf73d6d620d531a6d5e4261b34e5436a","tid":205082,"uid":8574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T13:59:34.000Z","msg":"正評 推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ba03d73efc7d17c0ea1895b8d36b3cfc70fdba9","tid":205082,"uid":53466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T14:01:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"27f329a9f17fbdde66ceb3869136b43e1151b2fa","tid":205082,"uid":13294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T14:30:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主不如你開個自殺post<br />\n<br />\n唔係點引人注意</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n講啲咁既野，毫無意義"},{"pid":"397c3255573659f96249f5d065cd3c2463972c53","tid":205082,"uid":6752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T14:32:50.000Z","msg":"個個跟風玩野，串多兩句又威脅你教唆自殺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n當e度facebook咩"},{"